          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter><html:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {A}]]></fr:tex> be a <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-0010.xml" title="Path object" addr="forest://erct/erct-0010" type="local">path object</fr:link>, and let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {B}]]></fr:tex> be a <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-0012.xml" title="Displayed path object" addr="forest://erct/erct-0012" type="local">displayed path object</fr:link> over <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {A}]]></fr:tex>. Then the <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-004H.xml" title="Total reflexive graph" addr="forest://erct/erct-004H" type="local">total reflexive graph</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {A}.\mathcal {B}]]></fr:tex> is a path object.</html:p>
 
   
